Louise Redknapp has taken to Instagram to post an emotional farewell to her son Charley as he prepares to head off to University. The Eternal singer, 47, branded her eldest son, 17, with ex-husband Jamie Redknapp her "best friend" as she paid tribute to him as he celebrated reaching a milestone. In view of her 747,000 followers, Louise wrote: "So proud of my boy and my best friend @CharleyRedknapp. "School leavers dinner tonight. Next stop Uni Xxx," she added alongside a row of crying emojis. The sweet snaps showed Charley looking dapper in a suit and purple bowtie while Louise displayed her toned legs in a red and blue floral mini dress.